The paper deals with the enumeration of matrices satisfying certain algebraic and logical constraints, which is a problem in discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The use of SAT solvers and computer algebra systems also suggests categories such as numerical analysis (cs.NA) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The paper also involves combinatorial algorithms (cs.DS) and logic in computer science (cs.LO).
